<br>
But if I were coding the change, and given the previous tendancies of Verant, I'm pretty sure what would happen is this ...<br>
<br>
No retroactive change. You log in on day and if you're in a hell level, the amount of experience you get per kill is upped by the modifier percent. So at level 40, you go from a 1.1 to a 1.2 modifier. A bit of code would be put in to give you that &quot;lost&quot; bit of experience.<br>
<br>
